# Summary
This documentation describes the Session Replay Plugin for Segment, which enables one-line integration between Segment's Amplitude (Actions) destination and Amplitude's Session Replay, including installation instructions, configuration options, and how it maps Segment user IDs to Amplitude device IDs.

